7TIP4s4%3D&h=612f42ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/internationalforhk</a><br />\nDM <a href=\"http://t.me/tylerdurdennnnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftylerdurdennnnn&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=7b346690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/tylerdurdennnnn</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZ0JyXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZ0JyXz.jpg&h=4b206eda&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"Hello we are from Brain problem team. We are launching a freelance journalist platform aiming to deliver more reader-journalist interaction through democratic journalism, censorship proof information distribution, and crowdfunding of reporting<br />\n<br />\nBy decentralizing press organization and giving individual journalist more independence, they will be less likely to self censor<br />\n<br />\nFreelance journalists can submit content and create accounts where users can subscribe to them and give them funding for news investigation <br />\n<br />\nUsers can make accounts, submit content, vote on content, suggest topics to be covered, and donate/subscribe/tip/crowdfund journalists/articles/crowdfunding topics<br />\n<br />\nThe platform ' editorial board will curate what content is on the front page, with user votes, our goal, to improve interaction and prevent censorship whether overt or self applied<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1564044/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1564044/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nWe are launching a crowdfunding campaign next week. We hope freelances journalists would make a good use of the platform and make this happen!!!!"},{"pid":"d8e9fa7a466061e247413bbb230413e09047467c","tid":1563551,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"2019年9月29日會唔會係全球最多人遊行集會既一日？？再次震撼全球<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以令多啲外國人知"},{"pid":"132e7e78e19e414c65872261716c8c806bf45ebe","tid":1563551,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"560fb86f228711c6bbe4b97b13bf7660084b184c","tid":1563551,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a3557a71f45f9955f9f33250f6dd13fa69a2c26","tid":1563551,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:55:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a17cd2586b0b83fd06e86e8f2f62542147f21f1a","tid":1563551,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c884b03c1a8fcef415db3a6470364625743f9ea0","tid":1563551,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"Send the request to or contact the Chinese ( non mainland china) / Taiwan /<strong><ins> Hong Kong Student Associations of <strong><ins>all colleges</ins></strong> in foreign countries.</ins></strong>  Hopefully you have some warm contacts, otherwise find the contact info. from the college web site, and send the requests to those cold contacts and ask them for referrals too....<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>All colleges in HK have<strong><ins> Alumni Associations around the world</ins></strong></ins></strong>. Ask the HK alumni office if they have help give you the contact information. <br />\n<br />\nAll big <strong><ins><strong><ins>high schools in HK also got Alumni Associations</ins></strong></ins></strong> in foreign countries too.  E.g. La Selle, Pui Ching, DBS, DGS, etc...<br />\n<br />\nLet me know if you cannot find those information."},{"pid":"d66de0c169cb93b4d657b0298d36ee73f9fe9080","tid":1563551,"uid":196771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0